Main KPI 13
  1. Click under Visualizations panel on Card
  2. Click and drag .CA Confirmed Field onto the Shared Axis for Card where it says "Add data fields here"
  3. Repeat for .CA Death  / .CA Existing / .CA Recovered

Then click on the Paintbrush (Format) icon under the visualizations pane and configure as seen below


NOTE*** Only difference between these KPIs are the color, General settings (location on grid except for Total Cases which doesn't have a Shadow) and Shadow settings. Also be sure to change the titles appropriately along with Display Units under Data label
